<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>prometheus on Aiden's Laboratory</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/tags/prometheus/</link><description>Recent content in prometheus on Aiden's Laboratory</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><copyright>Copyright © 2020-2021, Jongseob Jeon; all rights reserved.</copyright><lastBuildDate>Mon, 10 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/tags/prometheus/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>prometheus와 grafana 연결하기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/grafana/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/grafana/</guid><description>
&lt;p>이번 포스트에서는 local에서 실행한 seldon-core의 metric을 prometheus의 metric을 grafana에서 확인하는 방벙에 대해서 설명합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h1 id="grafana">Grafana&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>grafana를 설치합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>brew install grafana
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>grafana를 실행하기 위해선 아래 명령어를 입력합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>grafana-server --config&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/usr/local/etc/grafana/grafana.ini --homepath /usr/local/share/grafana --packaging&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>brew cfg:default.paths.logs&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/usr/local/var/log/grafana cfg:default.paths.data&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/usr/local/var/lib/grafana cfg:default.paths.plugins&lt;span class="o">=&lt;/span>/usr/local/var/lib/grafana/plugins
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>실행 후 &lt;a href="http://localhost:3000/">http://localhost:3000/&lt;/a> 에 들어갑니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-1.png" alt="img-1">
아이디와 비밀번호는 기본적으로 &lt;code>admin&lt;/code> / &lt;code>admin&lt;/code> 입니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>로그인 후 톱니바퀴에서 data source를 선택합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-2.png" alt="img-2">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>prometheus를 선택합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-3.png" alt="img-3">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>http 의 url에 &lt;a href="http://localhost:9090/">http://localhost:9090/&lt;/a> 를 입력합니다&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-4.png" alt="img-4">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Save &amp;amp; Test를 눌러서 저장합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>이제 새로운 대쉬보드를 만듭니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-5.png" alt="img-5">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>add an empty panel 을 클릭합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-6.png" alt="img-6">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>데이터 소스를 Prometheus1로 바꿉니다.
&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-7.png" alt="img-7">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>metric이 활성화됩니다.
&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-8.png" alt="img-8">&lt;/p>
&lt;p>보고 싶은 metric들을 추가합니다.
&lt;img src="https://aiden-jeon.github.io/imgs/seldon/grafana-9.png" alt="img-9">&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>seldon-core와 prometheus local에서 사용해보기</title><link>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/prometheus/</link><pubDate>Mon, 10 May 2021 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://aiden-jeon.github.io/post/tech/seldon/prometheus/</guid><description>
&lt;p>이번 포스트에서는 local에서 실행한 seldon-core의 metric을 prometheus로 가져오는 방법에 대해서 설명합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="install-prometheus">Install Prometheus&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>mac에서는 brew를 통해서 쉽게 설치할 수 있습니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>brew install prometheus
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;p>그 외 다른 os 에서는 아래 링크를 참조해서 설치하면 됩니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://prometheus.io/download/">https://prometheus.io/download/&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>정상적으로 설치되었는지 확인합니다.&lt;/p>
&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">&lt;span class="ln">1&lt;/span>❯ prometheus --version
&lt;span class="ln">2&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">3&lt;/span>prometheus, version 2.26.0 &lt;span class="o">(&lt;/span>branch: non-git, revision: non-git&lt;span class="o">)&lt;/span>
&lt;span class="ln">4&lt;/span> build user: brew@BigSur
&lt;span class="ln">5&lt;/span> build date: 20210331-18:20:11
&lt;span class="ln">6&lt;/span> go version: go1.16.2
&lt;span class="ln">7&lt;/span> platform: darwin/amd64
&lt;/code>&lt;/pre>&lt;/div>&lt;h2 id="run-seldon-core">Run Seldon-core&lt;/h2>
